/deep/.ivu-input{
    font-size 13px!important;
}
.hot_imgs
    border-top 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05)
    .title
        padding 13px 0
        color #999
        font-size 12px
        border-bottom 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05)
    .list-box
        .item
            display flex
            margin-top 20px
            .move-icon
                display flex
                align-items center
                justify-content center
                width 30px
                height 80px
                cursor move
            .img-box
                width 80px
                height 80px
                img
                    width 100%
                    height 100%
            .info
                flex 1
                margin-left 22px
                .info-item
                    display flex
                    align-items center
                    margin-bottom 10px
                    span
                        width 40px
                        font-size 13px
                    .input-box
                        flex 1
    .add-btn
        margin-top 10px
    .upload-box
        display flex
        align-items center
        justify-content center
        width 80px
        height 80px
        background #ccc
        border-radius 5px
